#Team communication and instant messaging solutions are an integral part of any business environment today. As of 2020, the total number of users of Slack and Microsoft 
#Teams exceeded 20 million. 
#Some organizations might have compliance policies in place which do not allow them to use services managed by third parties. They will prefer solutions that can be 
#managed and hosted on servers controlled by them. The same will extend to communication solutions as well. This project is intented to great a customized Team Instant 
#messaging solution that is managed by an organization in their own private network.

Step 1
Step name:	Creation of VPC

Instructions	
1) Navigate to VPC using the Services button at the top of the screen
2) Select "Your VPCs" on the left side of the screen
3) Click on "Create VPC"
4) Enter the following fields :
Name: Project 1 VPC
IPv4 CIDR Block : 10.0.0.0/16
The rest of the options can be ignored
5) Select "Create VPC"
6) Select the VPC and click on Actions->Edit DNS hostnames
7) Enable DNS hostnames and click on Save
